extendedInfo.description: The First Federal Community Bank Mobile Banking App  â Safe, Secure and Convenient.  Banking anytime, anywhere.  Manage your finances on the go with quick and easy access to your First Federal Community Bank account information.FEATURES-View your account balances and details in real-time-View transactions:  See your recent transactions and search account history, as well as sort and search based on recent activity, dates, transaction description, check number and amount-Transfer Money:  Move your money between First Federal accounts or transfer money to and from external accounts-Business customers:  Submit ACH single payments/receipts and domestic wires, utilizing existing templates -Pay Bills:  Schedule, modify and or cancel bill payments on the go.-Find Us:  View First Federal ATM/Branch locations and information-Contact Us:  Send or receive secure messages with the bank, as well as attach images to secure messages; and One Touch dial connect you to our Main Office.-Check Rate:  View our competitive rates *To use this app you need to be a First Federal Online Banking Customer.  If you need to sign up:  Please visit onlinefirstfed.com **To use Mobile Bill Pay need to be a Bill Pay user through Online Banking first.
